<s1>
<ptxt>
From number stamped on connecting rod and its cap and alphabets stamped on crank web No.5, determine new standard bearing to be installed to connecting rod big-end inside, by referring to the table.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
For example, if number stamped on connecting rod and its cap is “1” and alphabet stamped on crank web No.5 is “B”, install a new standard bearing painted in “Black” to its connecting rod big-end inside.
</ptxt>
